    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute dream of a car! It's in such incredible shape that it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied this beauty since day one, so you won't find a single scratch or a speck of dust out of place. It drives like a total charm and is ready for its next big adventure. I'm so excited for whoever gets to take this home\u2014you're going to love it!",
